 <H1>Class Inheritance</H1> 
 <P><H2>Class Inheritance</H2>
</P>
<P><UL><LI>A TV is a kind of home electronics appliance<UL><LI>And so are radio, VCR, CD player, LD player</UL><LI>All appliances share common properties and behavior<UL><LI>They can play audio, be turned on/off, etc.<LI>They also exhibit some differences</UL><LI>One can construct a Home Electronics Appliance class<UL><LI>All appliances are derived from it<LI>This is called inheritance</UL><LI>Humans are good at classifying, building taxonomies<UL><LI>Corresponds to OO inheritance hierarchies</UL></UL></P>
